    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18-45 years old

          -  Skin prick test or RAS test and physical examination conclude that the patient will
             have a beneficial effect from specific immunotherapy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Other diseases except atopic disease

          -  Pregnancy
